Well Architect Framework

- Related to: 
  - Measure existing workloads.
  - Document existing workloads.
- List of best practice to apply to AWS.
- Items:
  - Operational Excellence:
    - Constant improvement (new deployments)
    - Automation (update & change management, templates)
  - Cost optimization:
    - Work with AWS Cost Explorer
  - Reliability:
    - Backup & store
    - Load balancing
    - Data replication
  - Permance Efficiency:
    - Performance monitoring (Cloudwatch)
    - Load balancing (ELB)
    - AutoScaling
  - Security:
    - VPN
    - AWS Certificate Manager (ACM)
    - IAM
    - S3 bucket encrypting
    - Usage auditing (CloudTrail)